724243f-a.text:
Water Street, south from Fletcher Street. Across the foreground runs Maiden Lane. The gas station at the left runs from Fletcher Street to Maiden Lane. Opened to view there is the warehouse building at the S. E. corner. On the right is another cleared area utilired as another gas station. This extends from Maiden Lane to Pine Street. See View 2 for details of this. Dominating the background
is the towering Farmers Trust Bldg.
June 16, 1940

P. L. Sperr
